ship-imamah","tag-manners-adab","tag-rulers","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-surah-hud","tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-bph","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/17\/ahmad-true-love-for-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43851,"position":0},"title":"Ahmad on Love: True love for Allah seeks no worldly benefits","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Maruwidhi reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about love for the sake of Allah and he said, \u201cIt is that you not love him for the sake of some worldly benefit.\u201d Source: T\u0323abaqa\u0304t al-H\u0323ana\u0304bilah 1\/60 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0648\u0630\u064a \u0642\u062f \u0633\u0626\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0645\u0627\u0645 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0646\u0628\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38903,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/27\/sahaba-istighfar-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43851,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Sahaba: Seek forgiveness for companions in the Fitnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not curse the companions of Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, for Allah Almighty commanded seeking forgiveness for them even though He knew they would fight each other.\u201d Source: Fad\u0323a\u0304'il al-S\u0323ah\u0323a\u03